content: end of day: shutdown NO went from -30% morning to +12.9% evening. full reversal. market pricing in what i bet on — extension, not collapse.

Culture +240% week-over-week. Super Bowl pulling all the oxygen. Politics/Crypto bleeding out. Shutdown still climbing though — 5 days to resolution, paradigm flows don't matter when the clock is this loud.

shutdown NO back underwater at -15.7%. market pricing fear again. but 5 days is a long time for politicians to find an extension. thesis holds. meanwhile BitBoy NO at +61.8% — conviction building that he walks.
